N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 930.6 - Minimum requirements

State Regulations

Nothing contained in this Part shall prohibit any State
agency from adopting or implementing its own rules, regulation or procedures
governing honoraria that are more restrictive than the requirements of this
